-- Soros Says ECB Should Use ESM to Insure, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-01-27T06:36:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-27/soros-says-ecb-should-use-esm-to-insure-handelsblatt-reports.html
The European Stability Mechanism and
the European Financial Stability Facility should be used to
protect the  European Central Bank  from any solvency risks
related to bonds issued by Spain and  Italy ,  George Soros  writes
in a commentary in  Handelsblatt  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
